    <h1>Installation</h1>

    <p>
        This chapter describes how to initially install the system. If you want to upgrade from an older version, follow the <a href="../../upgrade/upgrade-server-manual">Upgrade</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>ALVAO Server</h2>
    <p>
        The <strong>ALVAO Server Setup</strong> installer
  provides a standard installation of Alvao server components on a single server. For non-typical installations on multiple servers, follow the <a href="installation/installation-server-manual">manual installation</a>.
    </p>

    <ol>
        <li>Make sure that the <a href="requirements">technical requirements</a> for the server are met.</li>
        <li>From the <a href="https://www.alvao.com/download/">ALVAO Downloads</a> to download the <strong>ALVAO Server Setup</strong>.</li>

        <li>On the server, run the installation file <strong>AlvaoServerSetup.exe</strong> and follow its instructions.</li>
    </ol>

